s turning this logical, orderly, respectful system into a whirlwind of chaos and animosity what you call entertainment? I just don't see the point in it. What is so wrong with a rotation that you would support all out gank wars? How can this possibly better the game, for you or anyone else? Tell me how charging some poor chump that waited 18 months or more for his epic a whopping 200k in platinum is what this game is all about. I'm just a no-name cleric in a little bitty guild that wants to test it's mettle against this dragon called Ragefire. I don't want to screw anyone over, or be screwed over in the process. Is that so unreasonable? So much so that destroying an agreement that was made only recently will be a better alternative?<br>
